{"id": 1688, "genre": 1001, "title": "最近你都有过哪些很“尬”或被“尬”的经历？", "description": "尬，原指互相较量、比试，现多用于描述令旁观者为之尴尬的硬来举动，比如尬聊、尬撩、尬发自拍等等。", "record_count": 3889, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170515144657XWdRHyqsEK80m1nc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-17T03:00:01Z", "options": [{"id": 204544, "content": "和同学撞了PPT的内容 我们完全不知道对方要做什么 结果就\"撞衫\"了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703550}, {"id": 205058, "content": "认错人永远是最尴尬的。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014928}, {"id": 204547, "content": "把天聊死了而自我感觉良好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893972}, {"id": 204549, "content": "地铁里手机没电了，对着自动关机的屏幕发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937443}, {"id": 204551, "content": "招~收~打~zì~员。1ooo字3o元。报酬曰结。打zì要求。错别字少，认真仔细，时间自由，学森宝妈无业游民等，均可. 联系企鹅:③②②⑨⑥④③⑤⑨⑤做与不做了解一下不会错", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034144}, {"id": 214535, "content": "骑自行车自己把自己跘倒了，成功飞行半米远头落地，把我吓坏了幸好没把马路砸坏掉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679333}, {"id": 214536, "content": "骑自行车自己把自己跘倒了，成功飞行半米远头落地，把我吓坏了幸好没把马路砸坏掉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679333}, {"id": 204553, "content": "一直把她当做好朋友，然后知道了朋友也有亲疏有别，不及他人之于她重要，做过的一厢情愿的事情都很尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985014}, {"id": 204554, "content": "感觉人生真的很迷茫，但是又很不甘心，到底要往那个方向去努力，才能达到自己想要的生活", "image": "img/option/option/20170517230443veCxT6dA5iRyXps2", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034153}, {"id": 204555, "content": "去别人家拉了屎?却冲不下去………………………", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334131}, {"id": 204556, "content": "就前几天，还读小学的表弟来我家玩，呆看着我用左手定则做物理题。我就觉得很尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033694}, {"id": 204557, "content": "微信和电话问“在干嘛呢”之类的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908062}, {"id": 205069, "content": "给他发一百条微信他只回复一个表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250675}, {"id": 204558, "content": "面基", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974719}, {"id": 207374, "content": "把一鸣的卡当成公交卡，怎么刷都没反应\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040326}, {"id": 204559, "content": "要毕业了，被在学校操场上偶遇到的陌生的带学生去演讲的老师，莫名其妙的邀请去他办公室喝茶，聊演讲，被问为啥空间没有我照片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034158}, {"id": 204815, "content": "拉个粑粑没纸，发微信求救，结果发错到女同事上，居然敲门给我送来了……那开门瞬间的一对视......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034662}, {"id": 204560, "content": "街上遇到很久不见的女生同学，看见她和一个男生走在一起。于是打招呼，你男朋友？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034158}, {"id": 205072, "content": "别人只是听电话，不是和你说话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977941}, {"id": 204561, "content": "参加朋友的婚礼时，高跟鞋一分为二，变平底鞋了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032215}, {"id": 204562, "content": "讲啥都没兴趣，真尬呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824059}, {"id": 204563, "content": "每天都在被减肥，还一直被羡慕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960560}, {"id": 205331, "content": "租房本以为躲开中介就可以了，结果还要一帮地盘军老太太赚介绍费，邻居为了脸面，必须通过她们，尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996595}, {"id": 204564, "content": "很生气很想一个人静一静的时候有人来惹你逗你笑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034173}, {"id": 204566, "content": "空间里自己转达自己的说说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974719}, {"id": 204567, "content": "和真正在乎的人对视", "image": "img/option/option/201705172327522VpByfWFeYbHwrnI.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364585}, {"id": 204823, "content": "塞着耳朵听歌，自以为小声的哼起来，直到同事全部扭过头来看着我……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 204825, "content": "啪啪啪时，突然一岁孩子坐了起来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 205337, "content": "啊~你今天涂粉了吧，好白啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948350}, {"id": 205850, "content": "自己被打鼾声吵醒，还以为谁闯进我房间了，睁眼看了一下没人，继续睡又打鼾了，这才知道原来是自己打鼾了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036093}, {"id": 204571, "content": "喝完酒 去尬聊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942625}, {"id": 204572, "content": "讲完笑话之后的冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213412}, {"id": 204573, "content": "唱歌的时候发现太大声，只能装作不在意继续把歌唱下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213412}, {"id": 204574, "content": "群里发消息没一个人理", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999605}, {"id": 207647, "content": "戴耳机听摇滚，朋友也要听 听几句便把耳机还给我说怎么在听鬼叫 爱听怪歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040648}, {"id": 204580, "content": "去学校打印店洗照片\n店内的人都知道和我合影的人是谁（异性）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034195}, {"id": 204581, "content": "硬讲一个笑话，别人没笑，把自己先笑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034199}, {"id": 204582, "content": "急着約會 沖涼沖一半停水", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979568}, {"id": 204583, "content": "玩老鹰捉小鸡 当母鸡 却把老鹰压在身下苦苦求饶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034203}, {"id": 204584, "content": "去学校打印店洗照片\n店内工作人员都知道合影的人是谁 \n其实没啥的 主要是异性", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034195}, {"id": 205608, "content": "和好友对嘴时被暗恋的人看到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036262}, {"id": 205097, "content": "每次一起出去 收到健身房广告传单的永远都是我……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012769}, {"id": 204586, "content": "找到一个超级好玩的点，可是大家都不懂你，只有你自己在嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034215}, {"id": 204587, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈，这留言简直fml大集锦！乐得不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 204588, "content": "几十个人对着你唱生日歌，真的不知道该做点什么，尬笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960911}, {"id": 204592, "content": "平时很粗鲁的人，在晚上和男友打电话嗲的要命，而且一个寝室人都在听\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863203}, {"id": 204593, "content": "老师来查寝手机响了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032406}, {"id": 204849, "content": "坐火车，5号车，结果上了11车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211089}, {"id": 204596, "content": "。。母亲在超市大喊我名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031714}, {"id": 205877, "content": "路上遇到经常看到却不打招呼的熟人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036806}]}